data.name: label5.Text
data.value: You can calculate this shift by taking a picture of the time displayed by your dive computer with your underwater camera and enter the time you read. You need to do this for each set of photos or trip.

data.name: label6.Text
data.value: To associate pictures and profiles, you need to know the shift between the clock of your dive computer and the clock of your camera. Picture timestamps are retrieved from the EXIF tag DateTimeOriginal.
